                    "subtype": "activation",
                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "effect": "The creature enters a simple stance that makes the most of the mat\u2019s stabilizing magic. While in this stance, if at least half of the creature\u2019s space is atop the mat, it cannot gain the off-guard condition.",
